28/10/2005
WASHINGTON, United States -- The US Defence Department on Wednesday (26 October) announced approval of the sale of 40 F-16 fighter jets and related equipment to Greece. 
The estimated value of the deal is $3.1 billion. 
Pentagon officials say the aircraft and equipment will enhance Greece's capabilities within NATO. 
(Kathimerini - 28/10/05; Reuters - 26/10/05)
